EXTRACTED VALUE: Tenchu Z is a pretty lousy entry to the series, and is one Xbox 360 title that doesn’t flex any next-gen muscle.
Circle of Doom’s problems all seem so frustratingly obvious the first time you see them that it makes you wonder why they were never changed.
Shrek the Third disappoints in every single category.
There's no reason to pick this one up, regardless of how bad you need a basketball fix--there are plenty of cheaper, better options available.
